### Youyu — Authentication & User
### Run this file after every change to auth, user profile, or verification endpoints.
### Wave 1 email-code variables must come from a local HTTP client environment.
### Do not commit real recipients, codes, SMTP credentials, or production secrets.

@baseUrl = http://localhost:8080
@registrationEmail = auth-wave1-register@example.test
@resetEmail = auth-wave1-reset@example.test

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# AUTH
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

### Send registration email code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/email-codes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{registrationEmail}}",
  "purpose": "register"
}

###

### Register new user after entering the received code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/register
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "username": "httptest01",
  "password": "{{registrationPassword}}",
  "nickname": "HTTP Test User",
  "email": "{{registrationEmail}}",
  "emailCode": "{{registrationEmailCode}}"
}

###

### Login — regular user (seed data)
# @name userLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "zhangsan",
  "password": "user123"
}

###

### Login - wrong password; repeat three times to trigger CAPTCHA escalation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "zhangsan",
  "password": "wrongpassword"
}

###

### Create graphical CAPTCHA challenge
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/captcha

###

### Login after CAPTCHA escalation
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "zhangsan",
  "password": "user123",
  "captchaChallengeId": "{{captchaChallengeId}}",
  "captchaCode": "{{captchaCode}}"
}

###

### Send password-reset email code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/email-codes
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{resetEmail}}",
  "purpose": "reset_password"
}

###

### Reset password after entering the received code
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/password-reset
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "{{resetEmail}}",
  "emailCode": "{{resetEmailCode}}",
  "newPassword": "{{resetNewPassword}}"
}

###

### Login - admin (seed data)
# @name adminLogin
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "admin",
  "password": "admin123"
}

###

### Get current auth context (mock token)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER

###

### Get current auth context — no token → expect 401 or empty user
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/auth/me

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# USER PROFILE
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Get own profile (authenticated)
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER

### Update own public profile nickname
PATCH {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "nickname": "Profile HTTP Test"
}

###

### Upload avatar image
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/avatar
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER
Content-Type: multipart/form-data; boundary=avatar-boundary

--avatar-boundary
Content-Disposition: form-data; name="file"; filename="avatar.png"
Content-Type: image/png

< ./fixtures/avatar.png
--avatar-boundary--

###

### Submit email binding
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/email
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "email": "profile-http-test@campus.edu.cn"
}

###

###

### Get own profile — no token → expect 401
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/profile

###

### Get privilege profile
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/privileges
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER

###

### List own addresses
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/addresses
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER

###

### Get own preference defaults/persisted settings
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/preference
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER

###

### Update own preference settings
PUT {{baseUrl}}/api/users/me/preference
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "themeMode": "dark",
  "themeColor": "fresh_green",
  "homeDisplayMode": "compact",
  "defaultFulfillmentType": "offline",
  "defaultPaymentMethod": "mock_payment",
  "defaultSortType": "latest",
  "notificationPreference": {
    "orderReminder": false,
    "reviewReminder": true
  }
}

###

### Add address
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/addresses
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "receiverName": "张三",
  "receiverPhone": "13800000001",
  "addressType": "campus",
  "campusArea": "北苑",
  "detailAddress": "1号楼101室",
  "isDefault": true
}

# ─────────────────────────────────────────────
# STUDENT VERIFICATION
# ─────────────────────────────────────────────

###

### Submit verification (user without approved verification)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/users/verification
Authorization: Bearer mock-1002-USER
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "studentNo": "20240002",
  "realName": "李四",
  "college": "外国语学院",
  "major": "英语",
  "grade": "2024级",
  "campusEmail": "lisi@campus.example.test"
}

###

### Get own verification status
GET {{baseUrl}}/api/users/verification
Authorization: Bearer mock-1001-USER

###

### Login - reviewer admin staff (seed data)
POST {{baseUrl}}/api/admin/auth/login
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "loginId": "reviewer",
  "password": "admin123"
}
